    public static interface Annotate.Worker
    A client that needs to run during Annotate.flush() registers an worker into one of the queues defined in this class. The queues are: Annotate.earlier(Worker), Annotate.normal(Worker), Annotate.typeAnnotation(Worker), Annotate.repeated(Worker), Annotate.afterRepeated(Worker), Annotate.validate(Worker). The run() method will called inside the Annotate.flush() call. Queues are empties in the abovementioned order.
